            <thetext>Emitting events is a necessary feature for a lot of objects. Therefore, the emitter is a important class we used as base class in the next branch quite often. But what if someone wants to extend from another object and still needs to have the event API. Therefore, we should move the emitter code to a mixin and use it that way as often as possible. The original emitter can still be valid for use cases where the emitter is used as it is like in qxWeb.</thetext>
